article_title: Katrina Anniversary Parade in New Orleans
article_text: Residents in the Lower 9th Ward in New Orleans gathered Saturday to hold a parade marking the 10th Anniversary of Hurricane Katrina. The massive storm, and the wide scale failures of the levee system left 80 percent of New Orleans under water. (Aug AP
